Class AccountResponsibility

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.kuali.rice.kns.bo.BusinessObject
public class AccountResponsibility
extends org.kuali.rice.kns.bo.TransientBusinessObjectBase
implements Serializable

This class holds respnsibility information pertaining to an account specifically whether or not the responsibility is of type Fiscal Officer, Primary Delegate of Fiscal Officer, or Secondary Delegate of Fiscal Officer, and if it is one of the delegated responsibility types, then there is additional information about the responsibility such as dollar range and document type
